text: Hildegard Grill (born 20 October 1927) is an Austrian gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1927 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Austrian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Austria Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
